Text: FINALLY!!!!!  Ricky, Julian and Bubbles moment of triumph.  you know you've made it when they make your life into a video game...LOL

there was an adult comedy series made in Canada about 3 fictional characters who live in a trailer park in the east coast.  the 3 brothers in the show are named Ricky, Julian and Bubbles.  it's basically an independantly produced show (done in a mock-umentary style).  very funny BUT definitely for adults.  just google it and check it out.  I keep forgetting that a lot of people outside Canada don't get to see the show.
